    {
        "id": "demo_info",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "manual_demo_tab",
        "name": "📖 MANUAL DEMONSTRATION FLOWS - Use with Expo Go",
        "info": "These flows work alongside manual app navigation.\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Start Expo Go app on emulator\n2. Click Node-RED buttons to control backend state\n3. Manually navigate app screens\n4. Watch real-time data sync\n\n**Scenarios:**\n- Normal Journey: Create trip → Navigate screens\n- Approaching Alert: Trigger GPS-based alert\n- Bus Break: Simulate passenger break\n- Disembark: Complete journey",
        "x": 300,
        "y": 20,
        "wires": []
    },
